				"id": "x2_37",
				"text": "<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>ATC-grupp</strong></div><p><strong><div class=\"tableLine\">Läkemedel <br></div><div class=\"tableLine\">som påverkar</div></strong></p></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>C3/C4</strong></div><p><strong><div class=\"tableLine\">Kombinationen kan kräva dos-<br></div><div class=\"tableLine\">anpassning av följande läkemedel</div></strong></p></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>D3/D4 </strong></div><p><strong><div class=\"tableLine\">Kombinationen bör undvikas pga <br></div><div class=\"tableLine\">påverkan på följande läkemedel</div></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">A02 antacida</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">B03 järn abs <span>↓</span></div><div class=\"tableLine\">H03 levotyroxin abs <span>↓</span></div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">J01 tetracykliner abs <span>↓↓</span></div><div class=\"tableLine\">J01 fluorokinoloner (ofloxacin<a class=\"tableFootnoteLink\" href=\"#fnote_26\"><sup>a</sup></a>, cipro-</div><div class=\"tableLine\">floxacin m fl) abs <span>↓↓</span></div><div class=\"tableLine\">J02 ketokonazol abs <span>↓↓</span></div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">A02 omeprazol</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">J02 ketokonazol abs <span>↓</span></div><div class=\"tableLine\">J02 flukonazol met <span>↓</span></div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">B01 klopidogrel eff <span>↓</span></div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">A02 sukralfat</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">H03 levotyroxin abs <span>↓</span></div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">J01 fluorokinoloner (ciprofloxacin m fl) </div><div class=\"tableLine\">abs <span>↓↓</span></div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">B03 tvåvärt järn<span class=\"tab\"></span></div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">C09 kaptopril abs <span>↓</span></div><div class=\"tableLine\">H03 tyroxin abs <span>↓</span></div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><span class=\"tab\"></span>J01 flu